data.text: Late 1970s re-release of TAKRL LP with plain white cover and colored title insert (yellow, orange, or purple). This is the same release as Cocksucker Blues. Title insert contains both old (TKRWM 1822) and new (TKRWM 1822-B) catalog numbers. Pale yellow labels with side delineations printed. Cover retains original shrink wrap. Beautiful unplayed condition, disc just has a slight storage warp not affecting play. Mild corner wear on cover.
